10. d5 { Not very critical. } 10... exd5 11. exd5 Bf5
{ This is the problem of 11.exd5 while @@StartFEN@@rnbqk2r/pp3ppp/8/P1pp4/1np1P3/2N2N2/1P3PPP/R2QKB1R w KQkq - 0 11@@EndFEN@@  11.Nxd5  N8c6!  ,  attacking a5, also does not inspire confidence. }
