Kxf8
{ White is lost since ...Ra8-d8 is coming and there are big threats connected to White's weakened king as well. We take with the king since  19...Rxf8  20.Re1  Bg4  21.Ne7+  Qxe7  22.Qxg4  gives White some fighting chances.  With the king on f8, there is no check on e7, and the same ...Bg4 move is lethal. }
