{ We aren't huge fans of  14...Bxd4  15.Qxd4  Bb7  16.Nxd5  exd5  17.Rad1  with good compensation for White, with f2-f4 coming,  but @@StartFEN@@r1b2rk1/p2n1ppp/2q1p3/1pbnP3/2pN4/2N1B1P1/PP3PBP/R2Q1RK1 b - - 2 14@@EndFEN@@  14...Qa6  as once played by Nils Grandelius may be a decent alternative. }
