{ Black has managed to get the perfect setup. We are following a 2017 correspondence game and will continue to do so for a few more moves. }
17. Bc4 Qc6 { 17...Qh5!?  is not out of the question either. } 18. Bb3 Rfd8 19.
Rfc1 { In case of  19.Rfd1  the waiting move  19...h6  looks fine. } 19... Qe4
