{ The critical continuation. } 22... Nd7 23. d5 Qg5
{ Black has adequate counterplay. } 24. dxe6
{ A bit greedy and not in the spirit of the position. } 24... Nc5 25. exf7+
Kxf7
{ Black has happily given up a pawn in order to bring the queenside forward. }
