Nd5 22. Re1 a4 { Black is okay here. } 23. e4 Ne7 24. Rxc3 Rfd8 25. Rc4 a3 26.
Nb4 Qa5
{ Black has good compensation. White's center is vulnerable and the a-pawn is very strong. }
