{ 11.Qc2  stops our knight from jumping to  e4  but is asking for trouble because of  11...e4  12.Ng5  O-O  when taking on e4 is very dangerous, opening up the e-file,  but  13.Be2  Re8  followed by ...h6 is great for Black as well. }
