Ka2 Nd5
{ Threatening to win the queen with ...Nd5-b4+ followed by ...Qd1-a1+. } 25.
Qa8+ Kd7 26. Qxh8 Nb4+ { This leads to mate. } 27. Ka3 Nc2+ 28. Ka2 Qa1+ 29.
Kb3 Nd4+ 30. Kc4 Qc1+ 31. Kb4 Qxb2+ 32. Kc4 Qb3+
{ After  33.Kc5  , Black can choose between three moves that all lead to instant mate. }
