Nc7+
{ White's position is beyond saving. After  9.Bc7  cxb5  or @@StartFEN@@r3kbnr/pb1n1ppp/1qp1p3/1N6/P1pP1B2/4PQ2/1P3PPP/R3KBNR w KQkq - 1 9@@EndFEN@@  9.Nd6+  Bxd6  10.Bxd6  c5  Black wins quickly. }
9... Kd8 10. Nxa8 Qxb2
{ Now we not only attack the rook but also threaten ...Bb4+ with mate to follow. This is far too much for White to handle. }
