6... exd5 7. Qb3
{ After slower moves we'd play ...c6, for example,  7.Bg5  c6  or @@StartFEN@@rn1qkb1r/ppp2ppp/5nb1/3p4/3P3N/2N5/PP2PPPP/R1BQKB1R w KQkq - 0 7@@EndFEN@@  7.g3  c6  . This type of Carlsbad structure is fine for Black.  After ...c6, we are always ready to answer Qb3 with ...Qb6. }
7... Nc6
