exd5 9. Qa4+ { White forces our knight to c6 and has a tactical shot in mind. }
9... Nc6 10. Ba6
{ Woah, this can be a nasty surprise... but given that you just learned that the move exists, it won't be one anymore! It turns out that White's move looks better than it is. }
